{"id":"sent-travel","type":"sentence","name":"旅行场景句","category":"场景表达","description":"围绕交通、酒店、餐厅和出行需求的实用句。","source":{"name":"Tatoeba","url":"https://tatoeba.org/","downloadsUrl":"https://downloads.tatoeba.org/exports/","license":"CC-BY 2.0 FR","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/fr/"},"items":[{"id":"book-sent-travel-25684-6822546","english":"Did you buy a round-trip ticket?","chinese":"你买了往返的票吗？","sourceIds":{"english":25684,"chinese":6822546}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-2540709-9955801","english":"Do you want another cup of coffee?","chinese":"你想要另一杯咖啡吗？","sourceIds":{"english":2540709,"chinese":9955801}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-813321-813320","english":"Would you like some tea or coffee?","chinese":"你想喝点儿咖啡或茶吗？","sourceIds":{"english":813321,"chinese":813320}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-70281-1516486","english":"You bought the ticket for the train?","chinese":"你买火车票了吧？","sourceIds":{"english":70281,"chinese":1516486}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-687390-5920099","english":"What room would you like to reserve?","chinese":"您想订什么房间？","sourceIds":{"english":687390,"chinese":5920099}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-18189-344190","english":"How far is it to the airport?","chinese":"到机场有多远？","sourceIds":{"english":18189,"chinese":344190}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-63922-334622","english":"Might I ask your name and address?","chinese":"我能问一下您的姓名和住址吗？","sourceIds":{"english":63922,"chinese":334622}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-813462-813452","english":"Tea or coffee - which would you like?","chinese":"你想喝咖啡还是喝茶？","sourceIds":{"english":813462,"chinese":813452}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-62256-9955801","english":"Would you like another cup of coffee?","chinese":"你想要另一杯咖啡吗？","sourceIds":{"english":62256,"chinese":9955801}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-325508-1446790","english":"I feel like going on a trip.","chinese":"我想去旅行。","sourceIds":{"english":325508,"chinese":1446790}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-435205-435209","english":"I hope you have a good trip.","chinese":"祝你一路平安。","sourceIds":{"english":435205,"chinese":435209}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-2471347-5611565","english":"Where is the key to this room?","chinese":"这房间的钥匙在哪里？","sourceIds":{"english":2471347,"chinese":5611565}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-6159779-6158478","english":"I want a bottle of ice water.","chinese":"我要一瓶冰水。","sourceIds":{"english":6159779,"chinese":6158478}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-255396-1446774","english":"I don't go to school by bus.","chinese":"我不乘公交去学校。","sourceIds":{"english":255396,"chinese":1446774}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-258198-346070","english":"I want to have my own room.","chinese":"我想要有我自己的房间。","sourceIds":{"english":258198,"chinese":346070}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-2716243-5574757","english":"I am going to water the horse.","chinese":"我要去饮马。","sourceIds":{"english":2716243,"chinese":5574757}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-7156437-330589","english":"I used a map during my trip.","chinese":"我在旅行中用了地图。","sourceIds":{"english":7156437,"chinese":330589}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-4430063-375320","english":"I get off at the next station.","chinese":"我下一站下车。","sourceIds":{"english":4430063,"chinese":375320}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-6841939-6956997","english":"Is the water in the glass clean?","chinese":"杯子里的水干净吗？","sourceIds":{"english":6841939,"chinese":6956997}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-261572-472868","english":"I don't have to clean my room.","chinese":"我不用打扫房间。","sourceIds":{"english":261572,"chinese":472868}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-1698674-11502945","english":"You can go to the bus station.","chinese":"你可以去巴士站。","sourceIds":{"english":1698674,"chinese":11502945}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-411906-505639","english":"I would like to drink a coffee.","chinese":"我想喝杯咖啡。","sourceIds":{"english":411906,"chinese":505639}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-35272-462033","english":"Will you show me your passport, please?","chinese":"能否请您给我看一下您的护照？","sourceIds":{"english":35272,"chinese":462033}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-253439-700945","english":"I don't put sugar in my coffee.","chinese":"我喝咖啡不加糖。","sourceIds":{"english":253439,"chinese":700945}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-13559155-801394","english":"I want to work in a restaurant.","chinese":"我想在餐廳工作。","sourceIds":{"english":13559155,"chinese":801394}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-18216-528024","english":"We saw her off at the airport.","chinese":"我们在机场为她送行。","sourceIds":{"english":18216,"chinese":528024}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-1553477-1783798","english":"I don't want to miss my train.","chinese":"我不想错过我的火车。","sourceIds":{"english":1553477,"chinese":1783798}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-5598513-5637331","english":"I'll take you to the bus stop.","chinese":"我会带你到公交车站。","sourceIds":{"english":5598513,"chinese":5637331}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-7834612-6158477","english":"I want a little bottle of water.","chinese":"我要一瓶小水。","sourceIds":{"english":7834612,"chinese":6158477}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-33358-760810","english":"Is the hotel close to the airport?","chinese":"酒店离机场远不远？","sourceIds":{"english":33358,"chinese":760810}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-26057-602929","english":"Is there a bank near the station?","chinese":"地铁站的附近有银行吗？","sourceIds":{"english":26057,"chinese":602929}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-38059-390439","english":"By the way, what is your address?","chinese":"对了，你的地址是什么?","sourceIds":{"english":38059,"chinese":390439}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-599205-794165","english":"I'd like to reserve a hotel room.","chinese":"我想要订房。","sourceIds":{"english":599205,"chinese":794165}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-13573048-333303","english":"I try to save room for dessert.","chinese":"我尽量留着胃吃甜点。","sourceIds":{"english":13573048,"chinese":333303}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-1230443-1753088","english":"How long will the train stop here?","chinese":"火车要在这里停多久？","sourceIds":{"english":1230443,"chinese":1753088}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-29361-4267353","english":"I should cancel my L.A. trip.","chinese":"我应该取消我到洛杉矶的旅行。","sourceIds":{"english":29361,"chinese":4267353}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-264242-375320","english":"I'll get off at the next station.","chinese":"我下一站下车。","sourceIds":{"english":264242,"chinese":375320}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-262212-180705","english":"I am looking forward to the trip.","chinese":"我很期待去旅游.","sourceIds":{"english":262212,"chinese":180705}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-2074261-333303","english":"I try to leave room for dessert.","chinese":"我尽量留着胃吃甜点。","sourceIds":{"english":2074261,"chinese":333303}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-446059-446057","english":"Why are there crickets in my room?","chinese":"我的房间里为什么有蟋蟀？","sourceIds":{"english":446059,"chinese":446057}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-279187-429417","english":"I left my umbrella on the train.","chinese":"我把雨伞留在电车上了。","sourceIds":{"english":279187,"chinese":429417}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-2490775-7768423","english":"We will take the train at eight.","chinese":"我们八点钟时坐火车走。","sourceIds":{"english":2490775,"chinese":7768423}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-3071865-9589451","english":"Excuse me, where is the taxi stand?","chinese":"请问，出租车站在哪里？","sourceIds":{"english":3071865,"chinese":9589451}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-4984126-457644","english":"How much does an entrance ticket cost?","chinese":"门票多少钱？","sourceIds":{"english":4984126,"chinese":457644}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-1216166-4267353","english":"I should cancel the trip to LA.","chinese":"我应该取消我到洛杉矶的旅行。","sourceIds":{"english":1216166,"chinese":4267353}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-270845-890633","english":"I'd like a glass of water, please.","chinese":"我要一杯水，謝謝。","sourceIds":{"english":270845,"chinese":890633}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-5150259-5150258","english":"Is the food at the restaurant halal?","chinese":"这个饭馆的菜是清真吗？","sourceIds":{"english":5150259,"chinese":5150258}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-35382-11254302","english":"It is cheaper to go by bus.","chinese":"乘巴士更省钱。","sourceIds":{"english":35382,"chinese":11254302}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-258188-375320","english":"I'm getting off at the next station.","chinese":"我下一站下车。","sourceIds":{"english":258188,"chinese":375320}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-866125-726467","english":"I drink water because I am thirsty.","chinese":"我喝水因为我渴了。","sourceIds":{"english":866125,"chinese":726467}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-18740-334028","english":"There is a bus stop near by.","chinese":"附近有个车站。","sourceIds":{"english":18740,"chinese":334028}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-311973-2031253","english":"She was in time for the bus.","chinese":"她赶上了巴士。","sourceIds":{"english":311973,"chinese":2031253}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-65393-746043","english":"Where do the airport buses leave from?","chinese":"机场大巴从哪里出发？","sourceIds":{"english":65393,"chinese":746043}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-253447-796687","english":"I spilled my coffee on the carpet.","chinese":"我把咖啡倒翻在地毯上了。","sourceIds":{"english":253447,"chinese":796687}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-1615236-1783780","english":"What I want isn't tea, but coffee.","chinese":"我要的不是茶，而是咖啡。","sourceIds":{"english":1615236,"chinese":1783780}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-4564210-3859480","english":"Is the movie theater near the station?","chinese":"电影院离电车站近吗？","sourceIds":{"english":4564210,"chinese":3859480}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-245548-471022","english":"What time does the first train leave?","chinese":"第一班火车什么时候出发？","sourceIds":{"english":245548,"chinese":471022}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-452580-452577","english":"I wanna have dinner in a restaurant.","chinese":"我想去饭店吃晚饭。","sourceIds":{"english":452580,"chinese":452577}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-3526285-3526284","english":"I booked a seat at this restaurant.","chinese":"我在这家餐厅订了位子。","sourceIds":{"english":3526285,"chinese":3526284}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-39471-333303","english":"I'm trying to save room for dessert.","chinese":"我尽量留着胃吃甜点。","sourceIds":{"english":39471,"chinese":333303}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-7633132-8905143","english":"I've already had two cups of coffee.","chinese":"我已经喝了两杯咖啡。","sourceIds":{"english":7633132,"chinese":8905143}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-5112670-13544343","english":"I usually drink my coffee with milk.","chinese":"我喝咖啡通常加牛奶。","sourceIds":{"english":5112670,"chinese":13544343}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-894926-333126","english":"There is a TV in this room.","chinese":"这个房间里有个电视机。","sourceIds":{"english":894926,"chinese":333126}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-4132515-792854","english":"This is the best restaurant I know.","chinese":"这是我知道的最好的餐馆。","sourceIds":{"english":4132515,"chinese":792854}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-12223755-334793","english":"We managed to catch the last train.","chinese":"我们能赶上最后一班火车。","sourceIds":{"english":12223755,"chinese":334793}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-300196-875375","english":"He asked for a drink of water.","chinese":"他要了水喝。","sourceIds":{"english":300196,"chinese":875375}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-57332-11698415","english":"I am quite comfortable in this room.","chinese":"在这个房间里我很舒服。","sourceIds":{"english":57332,"chinese":11698415}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-239234-798225","english":"It is not easy to train dogs.","chinese":"訓練狗是不容易的。","sourceIds":{"english":239234,"chinese":798225}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-1663458-1659165","english":"But that's not the last train, right?","chinese":"可是这不是最后一班火车，对吧？","sourceIds":{"english":1663458,"chinese":1659165}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-404265-404317","english":"Both of them are in the room.","chinese":"他们俩都在房间里。","sourceIds":{"english":404265,"chinese":404317}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-28809-8591268","english":"We were crowded into the small room.","chinese":"我们挤进了那间小房间里。","sourceIds":{"english":28809,"chinese":8591268}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-387566-334646","english":"Please give me a cup of water.","chinese":"请你给我一杯水。","sourceIds":{"english":387566,"chinese":334646}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-455787-736531","english":"I would like an air-conditioned room.","chinese":"我想要个有空调的房间。","sourceIds":{"english":455787,"chinese":736531}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-318839-2889801","english":"I helped my father water the flowers.","chinese":"我帮助我爸爸给花浇水。","sourceIds":{"english":318839,"chinese":2889801}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-251763-8703965","english":"There is no clock in my room.","chinese":"我的房间里没有时钟。","sourceIds":{"english":251763,"chinese":8703965}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-19640-476215","english":"Hurry, and you will catch the train.","chinese":"快一点，你就能赶上火车了。","sourceIds":{"english":19640,"chinese":476215}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-294097-10635234","english":"He took a taxi to the station.","chinese":"他打了个车去车站。","sourceIds":{"english":294097,"chinese":10635234}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-279212-347123","english":"The train is to arrive on time.","chinese":"电车将准点到达。","sourceIds":{"english":279212,"chinese":347123}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-5313708-2052722","english":"There's no need to hail a taxi.","chinese":"没必要叫出租车。","sourceIds":{"english":5313708,"chinese":2052722}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-10219951-10219956","english":"Although I haven't slept on the train.","chinese":"虽然我没在火车上睡觉。","sourceIds":{"english":10219951,"chinese":10219956}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-13559162-3526284","english":"I reserved a table at this restaurant.","chinese":"我在这家餐厅订了位子。","sourceIds":{"english":13559162,"chinese":3526284}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-997918-335009","english":"I can choose between tea and coffee.","chinese":"我可以在茶和咖啡之间做个选择。","sourceIds":{"english":997918,"chinese":335009}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-250147-353877","english":"Please give me a glass of water.","chinese":"请给我一杯水。","sourceIds":{"english":250147,"chinese":353877}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-1439942-1573098","english":"There are no tables in the room.","chinese":"房间没有桌子.","sourceIds":{"english":1439942,"chinese":1573098}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-62238-366829","english":"I'm afraid there isn't any coffee left.","chinese":"恐怕咖啡已經喝完了。","sourceIds":{"english":62238,"chinese":366829}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-49162-332746","english":"The meeting room is in use now.","chinese":"会议室正在使用中。","sourceIds":{"english":49162,"chinese":332746}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-33378-1735516","english":"You can use the hotel's swimming pool.","chinese":"你可以使用旅馆的游泳池。","sourceIds":{"english":33378,"chinese":1735516}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-294967-335227","english":"He took the wrong bus by mistake.","chinese":"他搭错了车。","sourceIds":{"english":294967,"chinese":335227}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-2847828-1323684","english":"The bus was late by ten minutes.","chinese":"公车晚了十分钟。","sourceIds":{"english":2847828,"chinese":1323684}},{"id":"book-sent-travel-453406-1307417","english":"This room is used as a kitchen.","chinese":"这房间是当厨房用的。","sourceIds":{"english":453406,"chinese":1307417}}]}